title: Project SAM - True Strike
description:
Torrent Info:
==============

This torrent is simply a repackaged version of another torrent I found online. I had to repackage it as the ZIP file included was broken (I had to spend some time fixing it), so I decided to upload an unzipped version instead.

The problem with this method is my fucking slow upload speed.


Torrent Contents:
==================

Compressed Samples (NKX)
Kontakt 5 instrument files (NKC, NKI)


Installation:
==============

Open Kontakt 5 (preferably the cracked version), click on "Add Library" and navigate to the downloaded folder.


Product Info:
==============

ProjectSAM's acclaimed TRUE STRIKE series holds the percussion libraries of choice for film, TV and game composers requiring cinematic, powerful percussion samples. TRUE STRIKE, the first volume in the series, focuses on orchestral percussion.

Offering 51 orchestral percussion instruments in multiple concert hall mic positions, TRUE STRIKE is the only orchestral percussion library you will ever need.

This new, re-released version of TRUE STRIKE has been completely re-designed for the Kontakt format. New features include a re-structured instrument list, a streamlined audio pool and a custom interface with on-screen ADSR control, instrument information and other options.
